    • updateView

      public void updateView(GameInfo info)
      updateView is the method that allows the update of the TUI. By getting the information from a GameInfo object points, goals, online players and all the additional information requested by the TUI regarding a specific game are updated by this method
      Parameters:
      info - represents the information that are needed for the update
